talent.description: Hello! I'm Hunikin, your emotional support doggo! I am an Australian shepherd vtuber who plays games, sings, draws, and shit posts.
talent.content: bork bork! I'm Hunikin, your emotional support doggo. I'm an Australian Shepherd VTuber from Canada who enjoys causing mayhem and chaos. Some of my favorite games are GTA, Minecraft, League of Legends, and Valorant! While my language may be mature and my sense of humor often dark, my goal is to help others by raising awareness of mental health issues!
